data.description: This well loved home in the Timberline community- has so much to offer.  No detail left undone. From all the outlet covers to the light fixtures, this beauty has been updated.  Just a few items to mention; in 2021 a new roof, new carpet and freshly painted.  The home has 4 mini splits providing which has proven to be very cost effective when regulating the temperature!  Light fixures have been replaced, new fencing and landscaping in the back yard, whole house surge protection and a new security/storm door - This is not your plain ole house, it has been loved and well taken care of!  Come enjoy the covered patio area, have enough room to work from home and have a space for children and a great entertainment floor plan!  This is a great home for a family- so much space!  Call today for an appointment!
